 how to do that is to stay away… because the one I have to protect him from is myself. \n\nI tried to be good. I always followed his lead. But last year, I got too needy. I got greedy. I asked for too much… and it pushed him away.\n\nCALEB: When my parents tell me they don’t trust me to stay home alone for the holidays, I’m not sure what they think I’ll get up to, but I’m not that surprised. After all, it’s not like they really know me. A point they only prove when they tell me that my big brother is finally coming home and that he’ll be in charge, and they say it sternly, like they actually think I might argue. \n\nThey don’t realize that it’s all I’ve ever wanted. Both to see Jonah again, and yes--God yes--to have him be in charge. I’ll be so good this time. I promise. Because I don’t think I can stand it if he leaves me again.\n\nMY BROTHER’S LOVE is a 24,000 word taboo gay romance novella with a happy ending that the boys in question really don’t care whether or not you approve of, because sometimes the wrong kind of love is exactly right when two hearts are as close as these.<\/span>\n  <a data-text-id=\"18174121054393074253\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"swapContent(\$(this));; return false;\">...more<\/a>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\'wtrButtonContainer wtrSignedOut\' id=\'8_book_45043745\'>\n<div class=\'wtrUp wtrLeft\'>\n<form action=\"/shelf/add_to_shelf\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" method=\"post\"><input name=\"utf8\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"&#x2713;\" /><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"orBKXmketm8jKqCKrTujpbOlbSA6jRlU3OjjzJzKTXzLdXQd1liC5UaJctpqk7DwgsFBgxzL/j0VGf7VJlkF6w==\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_id\" id=\"book_id\" value=\"45043745\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"name\" id=\"name\" value=\"to-read\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"unique_id\" id=\"unique_id\" value=\"8_book_45043745\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wtr_new\" id=\"wtr_new\" value=\"true\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_choice\" id=