<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer14871021150302244811"><b><u>Joseph</u></b> is a born and raised Southern Californian with a twenty-year stint of living in the Midwest. He loves the laid-back lifestyle of San Diego and considers himself lucky to live where people dream of vacationing.<br/><br/>A lifelong reader of m/m fiction, he began his writing career one night sitting at his MacBook and has never looked back. He writes to bring the characters he dreams about to life.<br/><br/><b><u>Visi</u></b></span>
